tle":"Hadith on Ease: The Prophet fears making Islam more difficult","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would abstain from doing a deed he liked to perform, fearing that people would do it until it became an obligation upon them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1076, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 717 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32498,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/how-angels-write-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":3153,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Deeds: Allah instructs angels how to record deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah says to the angels: If My servant intends to commit a sin, do not record it against him until he does it. If he does it, record it against him as one bad deed. If\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/13\/believers-die-plague-martyrs\/","url_meta":{"origin":3153,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Pestilence: Believers who die by plague are martyrs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"Decem